[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 166     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | AWS Lambda | Orchestration, marker detection, measurement computation |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      175[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | AWS Lambda | Orchestration, EXIF stripping, marker detection, measurement computation |
